channel.title: Changing Home, Portals and Teles
channel.description: I wanna change my Home to Edgeville, can someone help me? idk where to change coords, i look for the coords in client.java and it only says stupid stuff like "Deletethatobject"

item.title: Changing Home, Portals and Teles
item.dc:creator: @dwarvenknight dwarvenknight
item.description:
@dwarvenknight wrote:

Home: Go into Player.java and search for “initial” and change the coords.

Portals: Find the mortal inthe newObjects void. You may also have to search for the item ID to make it work. You should see like if itemID == **** and the coords which you should change.

Teleports are in clickingMost.
